<subSubSection id="F79D14A9CC3EFFEDFC76ECFB4908FBC7" box="[941,1323,1021,1046]" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph id="BF384722CC3EFFEDFC76ECFB4908FBC7" blockId="1.[941,1323,1021,1046]" box="[941,1323,1021,1046]" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">
<heading id="E470F04ECC3EFFEDFC76ECFB4908FBC7" allCaps="true" box="[941,1323,1021,1046]" centered="true" fontSize="10" level="1" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" reason="1">
“ 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFC62ECF8493CFBC4" baseAuthorityName="La Cepede" baseAuthorityYear="1802" box="[953,1311,1021,1045]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cynoglossidae" genus="Cynoglossus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bilineatus">
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFC62ECF8493CFBC4" bold="true" box="[953,1311,1021,1045]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">CYNOGLOSSUS BILINEATUS</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="F79D14A9CC3EFFEDFCF6EB38495FF804" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="BF384722CC3EFFEDFCF6EB384950FAC4" blockId="1.[813,1452,1085,1301]" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">
The fish referred to as “ 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFBFAEB3A4935FB87" baseAuthorityName="La Cepede" baseAuthorityYear="1802" box="[1057,1302,1087,1110]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cynoglossidae" genus="Cynoglossus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bilineatus">
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFBFAEB3A4935FB87" box="[1057,1302,1087,1110]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">Cynoglossus bilineatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” by authors is said to have been described by La Cepède (1802: 659, 663) as 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFC91EB7A482FFB47" authorityName="La Cepede" authorityYear="1802" box="[842,1036,1151,1174]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Achiridae" genus="Achirus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bilineatus">
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFC91EB7A482FFB47" box="[842,1036,1151,1174]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">Achirus bilineatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. There is no indication that La Cepède had examined material. His account included references to: (1) “ 
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFCB8EBBA4853FB07" box="[867,1136,1215,1238]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFCB8EBBA484FFB07" authorityName="Bloch" authorityYear="1787" box="[867,1132,1215,1238]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Pleuronectidae" genus="Pleuronectes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bilineatus">Pleuronectes bilineatus</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Linné, édition de Gmelin”; (2) “Bloch, pl. 188”; (3) “Pleuronecte, sole à deux lignes. Bonnaterre, planches de l’Encyclopédie méthodique”.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BF384722CC3EFFEDFCF6EA3B4FEEF947" blockId="1.[813,1452,1341,1686]" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">
Source (1) is 
<bibRefCitation id="DB163AD3CC3EFFEDFC13EA384895FA84" author="Gmelin, J" box="[968,1206,1341,1366]" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" pagination="1033 - 2224" refId="ref3361" refString="Gmelin, J. F., 1789. Caroli a Linne systema naturae per regna tria naturae, secundum classes, ordines, genera, species cum characteribus, differentiis, synonymis, locis. Beer, Lipsiae. vol. 1, pars 3: 1033 - 2224." type="journal article" year="1789">Gmelin (1789: 1235)</bibRefCitation>
. It explicitly refers to 
<bibRefCitation id="DB163AD3CC3EFFEDFCF6EA584FC6FAA7" author="Bloch, M" box="[813,997,1373,1398]" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" pagination="181 - 216" refId="ref3004" refString="Bloch, M. E., 1787. Naturgeschichte der Auslandischen Fische. Dritter Theil. Berlin. xii + 146 pp., pls. 181 - 216." type="book chapter" year="1787">Bloch (1787: 29</bibRefCitation>
, pl. 188). It includes no information not already appearing in Bloch’s text and therefore seems based exclusively on Bloch’s data. Moreover, it is not known that Gmelin had examined any material. Source (2) is plate 188 of 
<bibRefCitation id="DB163AD3CC3EFFEDFC95EAD84FC7FA27" author="Bloch, M" box="[846,996,1501,1526]" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" pagination="181 - 216" refId="ref3004" refString="Bloch, M. E., 1787. Naturgeschichte der Auslandischen Fische. Dritter Theil. Berlin. xii + 146 pp., pls. 181 - 216." type="book chapter" year="1787">Bloch (1787)</bibRefCitation>
; there is no mention of the text. Source (3) is 
<bibRefCitation id="DB163AD3CC3EFFEDFCABEAFB487FF9C7" author="Bonnaterre" box="[880,1116,1534,1558]" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" refId="ref3175" refString="Bonnaterre, [J. P.], 1788. Tableau encyclopedique et methodique des trois regne de la nature. Ichthyologie. Panckouke, Paris. lvi + 215 pp., 102 pls." type="book" year="1788">Bonnaterre (1788: 79</bibRefCitation>
, pl. 91 fig. 377). The figure is a black and white copy of Bloch’s figure. The description is that given by Bloch. There is also explicit reference to the French edition of 
<bibRefCitation id="DB163AD3CC3EFFEDFBC0E95848FAF9A7" author="Bloch, M" box="[1051,1241,1629,1654]" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" pagination="181 - 216" refId="ref3035" refString="Bloch, M. E., 1788. Ichtyologie ou histoire naturelle, generale et particuliere des poissons. Sixieme partie. De La Garde, Berlin, Didot, Paris &amp; White, London. viii + 151 pp., pls. 181 - 216." type="book chapter" year="1788">Bloch (1788: 21)</bibRefCitation>
, but no mention of inner anatomy.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BF384722CC3EFFEDFCF6E9BB495FF804" blockId="1.[813,1452,1725,2006]" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">
In conclusion, La Cepède’s account of 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFB14E9BA49B1F907" authorityName="La Cepede" authorityYear="1802" box="[1231,1426,1727,1750]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Achiridae" genus="Achirus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bilineatus">
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFB14E9BA49B1F907" box="[1231,1426,1727,1750]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">Achirus bilineatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is based only on Bloch’s 
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFBFCE9DA48F4F927" box="[1063,1239,1759,1782]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">
Pleur. 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFBB5E9DA48F4F927" authorityName="La Cepede" authorityYear="1802" box="[1134,1239,1759,1782]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Achiridae" genus="Achirus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bilineatus">bilineatus</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFB3CE9DA4988F927" authorityName="La Cepede" authorityYear="1802" box="[1255,1451,1759,1782]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Achiridae" genus="Achirus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bilineatus">
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFB3CE9DA4988F927" box="[1255,1451,1759,1782]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">Achirus bilineatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was not, therefore, a new species but a new combination of 
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFC97E81A4FDFF8E7" box="[844,1020,1823,1846]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">
Pleur. 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFC48E81A4FDFF8E7" authorityName="La Cepede" authorityYear="1802" box="[915,1020,1823,1846]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Achiridae" genus="Achirus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bilineatus">bilineatus</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
. As a result, the name 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFB26E81A4945F8E7" authorityName="La Cepede" authorityYear="1802" box="[1277,1382,1823,1846]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Achiridae" genus="Achirus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bilineatus">
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFB26E81A4945F8E7" box="[1277,1382,1823,1846]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">bilineatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is not available for a species of 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFB97E83A48F0F887" authorityName="Hamilton" authorityYear="1822" box="[1100,1235,1855,1878]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cynoglossidae" genus="Cynoglossus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFB97E83A48F0F887" box="[1100,1235,1855,1878]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">Cynoglossus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="DB163AD3CC3EFFEDFB38E83B498FF884" author="Menon, A" box="[1251,1452,1853,1878]" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" pagination="1 - 129" refId="ref3584" refString="Menon, A. G. K., 1977. A systematic monograph of the tongue soles of the genus Cynoglossus Hamilton-Buchanan (Pisces: Cynoglossidae). Smithsonian Contributions to Zoology, 238: 1 - 129, pls. 1 - 21." type="journal article" year="1977">Menon (1977: 36)</bibRefCitation>
listed the synonyms of his “ 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFB94E85A4966F8A7" baseAuthorityName="La Cepede" baseAuthorityYear="1802" box="[1103,1349,1887,1910]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cynoglossidae" genus="Cynoglossus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bilineatus">
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFB94E85A4966F8A7" box="[1103,1349,1887,1910]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">Cynoglossus bilineatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”. Among these, the earliest available name for this species is 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFA96E87A484EF864" authority="Bleeker, 1851" authorityName="Bleeker" authorityYear="1851" class="Malacostraca" family="Plagusiidae" genus="Plagusia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadrilineata">
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFA96E87A4FE0F867" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">Plagusia quadrilineata</emphasis>
Bleeker, 1851
</taxonomicName>
, thus the valid name of the species is 
<taxonomicName id="78873CA1CC3EFFEDFC40E8BA495BF804" authority="(Bleeker, 1851)" baseAuthorityName="Bleeker" baseAuthorityYear="1851" box="[923,1400,1981,2006]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cynoglossidae" genus="Cynoglossus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="764" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="quadrilineatus">
<emphasis id="8DF39B30CC3EFFEDFC40E8BA48E5F807" box="[923,1222,1983,2006]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="764">Cynoglossus quadrilineatus</emphasis>
(Bleeker, 1851)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
